f61f50fd-e063-49bf-b21d-74ec760249bb Separate egg yolks from whites.

f61f50fd-e063-49bf-b21d-74ec760249bb Bottle and age for one month.

ae2e1643-aa1b-4052-9978-2c0bf0febb23 Filter and bottle.

7bcc532d-c6fb-4d7d-b4f5-e50805c4acd1 Macerate for 3 weeks. Shake gently the jar twice a week.

5bb88795-7cf0-496d-babd-8de1650dcd34 Cranberry infusion. Cut 300 g cranberries into halves and cover with 600 ml of 50% alcohol.
5bb88795-7cf0-496d-babd-8de1650dcd34 Macerate for 3 weeks. Shake the jar every few days. Strain and filter.
5bb88795-7cf0-496d-babd-8de1650dcd34 Mix 500 ml of cranberry infusion with 200 ml of ginger infusion. Add 300 ml of sugar syrup and vanilla and lemon extracts.
5bb88795-7cf0-496d-babd-8de1650dcd34 Add water if needed to 1 liter mark. The recipe is for one liter of the product.

f14aef78-44d9-4e46-8f0c-3f8485a7edef Mix sugar with egg yolks until creamy and perfectly smooth.

f14aef78-44d9-4e46-8f0c-3f8485a7edef Continue mixing and start adding slowly 75° alcohol.
f14aef78-44d9-4e46-8f0c-3f8485a7edef Bottle and age one month.

a1a4bfa3-d555-4987-ac3d-040366e8d64d Continue mixing and add vanilla infusion and alcohol.
a1a4bfa3-d555-4987-ac3d-040366e8d64d Bottle and age for one month.

6293556a-bd21-4329-ac67-0de102cd0b56 Remove from heat, keep on stirring and add alcohol.
6293556a-bd21-4329-ac67-0de102cd0b56 Pour into bottles. You may serve Krupnik the moment it is done, but its taste improves in time.

b740ad6f-fedc-465c-ab20-7e6145062d59 Add sugar and alcohol.

c5e46200-e094-45a5-8e4d-628c8ac0100b Stir the contents and add water to 1 liter mark.
c5e46200-e094-45a5-8e4d-628c8ac0100b Bottle and age for one week.
